                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201206-99-off613 t18201206-99-cd614"></join>, one watch, value 8 l.; one chain, value 2 s.; one seal, value 6 s.; and one key, value 2 d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18201206-99-victim987" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Kidd
                        <interp inst="t18201206-99-victim987" type="surname" value="Kidd"></interp>
